properties.name: Marine Travel
properties.description:
Marine Travel is a Danish specialised travel agency that has been providing targeted and individually customised travel solutions within the areas of marine traffic, business travel, offshore traffic and alternative energy projects, including windmill and solar energy, since 1991. Employing more than 30 dedicated and experienced staff members at four locations in Denmark and Germany, Marine Travel is ready to serve our customers 24/7 all year round.

By applying the most modern booking system on the market, as well as providing a 24-hour emergency service that is only manned by our own highly qualified staff, we guarantee flexibility, lucrative prices and optimal consultancy services to all our customers – also in stressful periods and when unexpected events happen throughout the world.
Marine Travel is an authorised IATA travel agency that only cooperates with approved airline companies and low cost carriers that prioritise efficiency, quality and satisfied customers – just like we do.

Apart from our own offices we also have a network of close cooperation partners throughout the world. At Marine Travel, attentive customer service, lucrative tickets and flexible travel solutions make up the cornerstone in a dynamic industry that never stops to rest.

In short: Marine Travel moves people.
